title: Black Founders Bundle Order ships & arrives separately | 12 items
description: Everything in this mouthwatering collection comes from a Black-owned or Black-founded business. Try Mini Grahams and Vanilla Wafers from Partake, an allergy-friendly brand that partners with organizations to fight food insecurity. Sip on a cup of coffee brewed with BLK & Bold’s Medium Roast—founded by two friends, it’s a mission-driven company that donates 5% of its gross profits to nonprofits across the country. That’s not all: This bundle also features snacks made with heirloom corn from PipCorn, uplifting tea from Steepers Only, and super flavorful seasoning blends from the husband-and-wife-run brand Station 1923.

